&lt;h4&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage prospects from lead to close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearly articulate and demonstrate our value proposition, creating excitement and enthusiasm among prospects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate long-term relationships with customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain weekly sales forecast and achieve quota quarterly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run and implement 7 to 10 day pilot program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
