&lt;p&gt;At Gong, you will join a company built on innovative products, ambitious goals, and passionate people. We are shaping the future of revenue intelligence and we want people who are excited to build what comes next. You will work with a team that dreams big, moves fast, and cares deeply about the craft and about each other. Here, transparency and trust are core to how we operate, and every person has the opportunity to make a visible impact. If you want to grow, stretch, and do work that truly matters, Gong is the place to do the best work of your career.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Commercial Revenue Architects at Gong are strategic partners to our customers. Focused on driving revenue transformation from Gong’s AI Operating System. You’ll guide executive stakeholders and operational teams to drive revenue with Gong by architecting workflows, accelerating adoption, and realizing business results across the entire revenue lifecycle.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You will combine a deep understanding of how revenue teams operate with leading change management strategy to help customers operationalize the use of Gong into tangible business results. Your success is measured by activation and adoption, key persona engagement, customer value realization, and revenue impact (retention and expansion).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Revenue Transformation Strategy: Partner with senior GTM leaders to design and execute strategies that modernize their revenue operations through Gong’s AIOS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Workflow Architecture: Map current-state customer processes to AI-driven workflows that translate to revenue outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adoption and Change Management: Execute adoption initiatives that drive behavior change and embed Gong into daily team rhythms&lt;/li&gt;
