&lt;p&gt;At Gong, you will join a company built on innovative products, ambitious goals, and passionate people. We are shaping the future of revenue intelligence and we want people who are excited to build what comes next. You will work with a team that dreams big, moves fast, and cares deeply about the craft and about each other. Here, transparency and trust are core to how we operate, and every person has the opportunity to make a visible impact. If you want to grow, stretch, and do work that truly matters, Gong is the place to do the best work of your career.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As an Enterprise Account Executive, you’ll fill a key role in acquiring new customers and creating raving fans. Being a champion of the entire sales process from start to finish, you will use your creative prospecting skills to strategically pursue net new business. Working through complex deals, your insatiable curiosity makes you a thought leader, and your drive to succeed keeps you at the top of the leaderboard. Out-of-the-box thinkers and those who will never settle for the status quo are strongly encouraged to apply!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a part of Gong’s sales team, you will become a master of discovery &amp;amp; a strategic business partner for prospective customers. You will play a huge role in our company&#39;s growth while navigating your own individual growth journey as well. Are you looking for the opportunity to make big waves &amp;amp; to perfect your craft of sales? We can’t wait to meet you!&lt;/p&gt;
