&lt;p&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Orchestration Strategy
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the holistic strategy for how data flows across systems (SFDC, enrichment tools, AI tools, Gong,etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define how data is created, updated, validated, enriched, and consumed across GTM workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistency, scalability, and clarity in data ownership and data movement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
