&lt;li&gt;Design and own the enrichment framework (firmographics, technographics, intent, personas, buying groups, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Determine where enrichment happens, what tools are used, and how it is validated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance automation, accuracy, cost efficiency, and business value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead Routing Stakeholder&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
