&lt;li&gt;Ensure routing rules align to segmentation, territories, verticals, and coverage models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Marketing Ops, Field Ops and GTM Systems to ensure speed, accuracy, and transparency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Account Data Ownership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the business owner for account-level data integrity and partner with the territories team on account data requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the territory team and provide data supported recommendations on&amp;nbsp; account definitions, hierarchies, segmentation, industry classification, and account status logic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Process, Change Management &amp;amp; Communication&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own change management for any data model or process updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create clear communication plans, documentation, and rollout strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure stakeholders understand what is changing, why it matters, and how to use it across the organization including Finance, Data, SysOps, Marketing Operations and the full GTM Operations team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Forward-Looking Data Strategy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with RevOps and Finance leadership to define where data strategy needs to be in 6–12–24 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate and support analysis on future GTM needs (AI readiness, automation, segmentation evolution, new products, new routes to market).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data foundations are built with scale and flexibility in mind.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Workflow Integration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data is embedded directly into seller and manager workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and partner with the entire GTM Ops team to make data actionable, not passive.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize for adoption, clarity, and speed to value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Controls &amp;amp; Governance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own strong data control processes:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Field-level governance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validation rules&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exception handling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auditability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear ownership models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a “single source of truth” mindset across the GTM ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
