&lt;p&gt;As a Lead Solution Engineer on the team, you will be instrumental in creating raving fans among our prospects and customers. Your focus will be on helping them understand how our platform can drive their strategic business initiatives across the organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
